stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Installed : snow app run
    Installed --> Initialized : v1.init()
    note right of Initialized
        ALTERs services with EAIs
        Creates webhook service function
        Discovers controld DNS for dashboard
    end note

    Initialized --> ServicesCreated : v1.create_services()
    note right of ServicesCreated
        Creates service_compute_pool (1-5 nodes)
        Creates runner_compute_pool (1-10 nodes)
        Creates workflow_stage
        Starts controld + dashboard
    end note

    ServicesCreated --> Running : Services ready

    Running --> Stopped : app.stop_app()
    note right of Stopped
        DROP SERVICE dashboard
        DROP SERVICE controld FORCE
    end note

    Stopped --> Running : v1.start_controld() + v1.start_dashboard()

    Running --> [*] : DROP APPLICATION
